token number\">20</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 06, 2021","slug":"/notes/Deeper-look-of-array()-and-apply()-in-R","title":"Deeper look of array() and apply() in R","abstract":"Recently my wife asked a question that how to understand 3-dimension array in R. And How to understand the apply() function when it is applied on multi-dimension array. After digging further, I think it is really interesing..."}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/notes/Deeper-look-of-array()-and-apply()-in-R"}}}